# Template Automation & Build Process Rules

## Overview
This rule defines the automation processes for managing HTML templates with dynamic data mapping from the Kraken Bar and Lounge data file, ensuring consistent and efficient content management across all pages.

## File Structure & Organization

### Template Files
- [index.html](mdc:index.html) - Homepage with hero slider, highlights, featured menu, locations, reviews
- [about.html](mdc:about.html) - About page with brand story sections and image gallery
- [contact.html](mdc:contact.html) - Contact page with location details, maps, hours, and ordering links
- [menu.html](mdc:menu.html) - Menu page with food gallery and menu sections
- [photos.html](mdc:photos.html) - Photo gallery with lightbox functionality and content sections
- [services.html](mdc:services.html) - Services page with service offerings and descriptions

### Data Configuration
- [Content-Website.txt](mdc:Content-Website.txt) - Master data file with all content in key-value format

